<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-10 pb-16 md:pt-12 md:pb-20 text-center">
  <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.15] mb-4">
    Strategy, execution, and support
  </h1>
  <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-slate)] max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8">
    A marketing agency with the experience to plan, the skills to deliver and the structure to support.
  </p>
  <a
    href="/contact"
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-paper)] border border-[var(--color-line)] px-6 py-3 text-base text-[var(--color-ink)] hover:border-[var(--color-slate)] transition-colors"
  >
    <span
      class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full shrink-0 ring-2 ring-white"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #f2789a 0%, var(--color-accent) 60%, #c72f5e 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 12px 2px rgba(232, 70, 124, 0.5);"
    ></span>
    What brings you here?
  </a>
</div>
